<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>회원가입(자바스크립트 정규표현식은 직접 반영)</title>
</head>
<body>
    <form id="join_form" action="/joindb" method="post">
        <div>
            <label for="memberid">아이디</label><input id="memberid" type="text" name="memberid" />
        </div>
        <div>        
            <label for="memberpass">비밀번호</label><input id="memberpass" type="password" name="memberpass" />
        </div>
        <button type="submit">회원가입</button>
        <a href="/">취소</a> <!-- 회원가입을 하고 싶지 않다면 다른 a 태그 추가 가능 -->
    </form>
</body>
</html>